class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col font-sans\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#09090b] text-white\"><nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/[0.06] bg-[#09090b]/80 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-14 max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold tracking-tight\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"flex size-7 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap size-4 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div>AgentBeam</a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-400 transition-colors hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs\">Docs</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-400 transition-colors hover:text-white\" href=\"/login\">Sign In</a><a class=\"rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-blue-500\" href=\"/signup\">Get Started</a></div></div></nav><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0\"><div class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-[700px] w-[700px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/3 rounded-full bg-blue-500/15 blur-[150px]\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-[500px] w-[500px] translate-x-1/4 translate-y-1/4 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 blur-[150px]\"></div><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-1/2 h-[400px] w-[400px] -translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-blue-600/8 blur-[120px]\"></div></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-4 pb-24 pt-24 text-center md:pt-32\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-400\"><span class=\"inline-block size-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400\"></span>Now in public beta</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl\">The observability platform<!-- --> <span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">for AI agents</span></h1><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-400 md:text-xl\">Monitor traces, track costs, and debug issues across every LLM call your agents make.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/25 transition-all hover:bg-blue-500 hover:shadow-blue-500/40\" href=\"/signup\">Get Started Free</a><a class=\"rounded-lg border border-white/[0.1] bg-white/[0.03] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-300 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:text-white\" href=\"/login\">View Demo</a></div></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.01]\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 text-center\"><p class=\"mb-8 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500\">Built for teams shipping AI agents</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-12 gap-y-4\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600\">Acme AI</span><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600\">NeuralOps</span><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600\">StackAgent</span><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600\">Cortex Labs</span><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600\">SynthCo</span><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600\">AgentForge</span></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-24\"><div class=\"mb-16 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl\">Everything you need to ship agents with confidence</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-400\">From first trace to production monitoring — one platform.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div><div class=\"group relative rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 backdrop-blur-xl transition-colors hover:border-white/[0.1] hover:bg-white/[0.05]\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity size-5 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-semibold\">Real-Time Traces</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">See every LLM call, tool use, and agent decision as it happens. Full waterfall view of multi-step agent workflows.</p></div></div><div><div class=\"group relative rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 backdrop-blur-xl transition-colors hover:border-white/[0.1] hover:bg-white/[0.05]\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-dollar-sign size-5 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"2\" y2=\"22\"></line><path d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-semibold\">Cost Analytics</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">Know exactly what every agent costs. Per-model, per-agent cost attribution with budget alerts and optimization tips.</p></div></div><div><div class=\"group relative rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 backdrop-blur-xl transition-colors hover:border-white/[0.1] hover:bg-white/[0.05]\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-code size-5 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m16 18 6-6-6-6\"></path><path d=\"m8 6-6 6 6 6\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-semibold\">Auto-Instrumentation</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">Add 3 lines of code. Our SDK auto-captures Anthropic, OpenAI, and LangChain calls with zero config.</p></div></div><div><div class=\"group relative rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 backdrop-blur-xl transition-colors hover:border-white/[0.1] hover:bg-white/[0.05]\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layout-grid size-5 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"14\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"14\" y=\"14\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"3\" y=\"14\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-semibold\">Agent Registry</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">Agents self-register on first trace. See all your agents, their status, error rates, and performance at a glance.</p></div></div><a href=\"/coming-soon/security-vault\"><div class=\"group relative rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 backdrop-blur-xl transition-colors hover:border-white/[0.1] hover:bg-white/[0.05]\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield size-5 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-semibold\">Security Vault<span class=\"rounded-full bg-zinc-800 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-zinc-400\">Coming Soon</span></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">Agent identity management, least-privilege access control, and full audit trails.</p></div></a><a href=\"/coming-soon/testing-lab\"><div class=\"group relative rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 backdrop-blur-xl transition-colors hover:border-white/[0.1] hover:bg-white/[0.05]\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flask-conical size-5 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 .245.96l5.51 10.08A2 2 0 0 1 18 22H6a2 2 0 0 1-1.755-2.96l5.51-10.08A2 2 0 0 0 10 8V2\"></path><path d=\"M6.453 15h11.094\"></path><path d=\"M8.5 2h7\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-semibold\">Testing Lab<span class=\"rounded-full bg-zinc-800 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-zinc-400\">Coming Soon</span></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">Regression testing, A/B testing, and eval-gated deployments for your agent prompts.</p></div></a></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.01]\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-24\"><div class=\"mb-16 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl\">Up and running in 60 seconds</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-400\">Three steps. No config files. No infra to manage.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-500/10 text-sm font-bold text-blue-400\">1</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">Install the SDK</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-white/[0.06] bg-[#0c0c0e] p-4 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300\"><pre class=\"whitespace-pre-wrap\">pip install agentbeam\n\nimport agentbeam\nagentbeam.init(api_key=&quot;ab_...&quot;)</pre></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-500/10 text-sm font-bold text-blue-400\">2</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">Run your agents</h3></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 items-center rounded-lg border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">Your existing code works unchanged. We auto-capture everything.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-500/10 text-sm font-bold text-blue-400\">3</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">See everything</h3></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 items-center rounded-lg border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">Real-time dashboard shows traces, costs, and agent health.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-24\"><div class=\"mb-16 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl\">Simple, transparent pricing</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-400\">Start free. Scale when you need to.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"relative flex flex-col rounded-xl border p-6 backdrop-blur-xl transition-colors border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03]\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">Free</h3><div class=\"mt-2 flex items-baseline gap-1\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold\">$0</span><span class=\"text-zinc-500\">/mo</span></div></div><ul class=\"mb-8 flex flex-col gap-3\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check size-4 shrink-0 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>50K traces</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check size-4 shrink-0 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>3 agents</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check size-4 shrink-0 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>7-day retention</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check size-4 shrink-0 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>Community support</li></ul><div class=\"mt-auto\"><a class=\"block w-full rounded-lg py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold transition-colors border border-white/[0.1] bg-white/[0.03] text-zinc-300 hover:bg-white/[0.06]\" href=\"/signup\">Get Started Free</a></div></div><div 